brams-Swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Abrams-Swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Abrams-Swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Abrams-Swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">格雷西·艾布拉姆斯 (Gracie Abrams)</a>回顾了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>(Taylor Swift) 即将结束的大型<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/taylor-swift-live-in-edinburgh-3763814">“Eras 巡演”</a> ，并表示最后一场演出感觉就像“学校的最后一天”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swift-eras-tour-end-impact-3820896">泰勒·斯威夫特的 Eras 巡演结束：看看其巨大的全球影响力</a></strong></li></ul><p>艾布拉姆斯与斯威夫特一起参加了这一系列庞大巡演的最后一站，并在 12 月 8 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swift-perform-with-gracie-abrams-on-final-eras-tour-leg-in-vancouver-3820127">于加拿大温哥华举行的最后一场预定演出</a>中为这位流行偶像开场。</p><p>现在，在一次新的采访中，她反思了与斯威夫特一起约会的感觉以及看到演出结束的感觉。</p><p> “每个人都哭了一整天。这感觉就像是学校后台的最后一天，”她告诉<a href="https://www.nylon.com/entertainment/gracie-abrams-thats-so-true-interview-tour-new-album" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>尼龙</em></a>。 “每个人都带着他们的[巡演]书籍走来走去，互相签名。我们都带着记号笔四处走动。”</p><p>此次巡演总共持续 21 个月，共演出 149 场，标志着这位歌手、词曲作者和吉他手的新高点。它还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-brings-in-record-breaking-2billion-3820379">打破了巡演史上票房最高的记录</a>，据报道自开演以来收入达 22 亿美元（17.3 亿英镑）。</p><p>去年12月，巡演进行到一半时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-is-the-first-to-ever-gross-1billion-3556365">斯威夫特创造了历史，巡演成为首个票房收入达到10亿美元</a>（7.96亿英镑）的巡演。此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-to-become-the-most-lucrative-tour-in-history-3515012">有人预计，此次巡演一旦结束，将成为音乐史上最赚钱的一次</a>。全球共有 10,168,008 人观看了“Eras”演出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3820902" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3820902" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3820902" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/taylor-swift-eras-tour-gracie-abrams-credit-getty-images@2000x1270.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特和格雷西·艾布拉姆斯在多伦多的 Eras 巡演中一起表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/taylor-swift-eras-tour-gracie-abrams-credit-getty-images@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/taylor-swift-eras-tour-gracie-abrams-credit-getty-images@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/taylor-swift-eras-tour-gracie-abrams-credit-getty-images@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/taylor-swift-eras-tour-gracie-abrams-credit-getty-images@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/taylor-swift-eras-tour-gracie-abrams-credit-getty-images@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/taylor-swift-eras-tour-gracie-abrams-credit-getty-images@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3820902" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特和格雷西·艾布拉姆斯在多伦多的 Eras 巡演中一起表演。图片来源：TAS2024/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>不仅仅是艾布拉姆斯反思了在上一场演出后与斯威夫特一起参加演出的感受。正如<em><a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/178684/Taylor-Swift-s-final-show-felt-like-last-day-of-school" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MusicNews</a></em>所强调的那样，伴舞 Kameron Saunders 也表达了这种感觉，并表示在温哥华演出后他无法停止哭泣。</p><p> “我还没有准备好用合适的词语来概括这整个经历和我生命中过去的两年，所以请大家耐心等待我，因为我正在指导如何最好地做到这一点......但我可以并且准备做的是向我的老板娘说声谢谢，”桑德斯在 Instagram 上的标题写道。</p><p> “泰勒！我的女孩！你已经把地狱从这艘船上开走了。如此优雅！！带着沉着、自信、心灵、激情、善良、勇敢和爱！与你在一起的每一秒，我都感到被看见、被尊重、被庆祝、被重视、被尊重……宝贝，我会在一生中任何时间、任何宇宙、任何地方追随你，”该帖子继续说道。 “夜复一夜地陪伴在你身边是我一生的荣幸！ … 我爱你！谢谢你！”</p><p>在最后一场“Eras Tour”演出中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swift-perform-with-gracie-abrams-on-final-eras-tour-leg-in-vancouver-3820127">斯威夫特与艾布拉姆斯一起登台</a>，两人爆发了艾布拉姆斯的“我爱你，对不起”和斯威夫特的“最后的吻”的二重唱，这首歌曲取自她2010年的专辑“现在讲&#39;。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDZ7A-9P4TY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C56