//www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-share-video-for-the-karate-kid-starring-ralph-macchio-3814143">歌曲《The Karate Kid》的音乐视频中</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/karate-kid-legends-first-trailer-brings-ralph-macchio-jackie-chan-together-3823388">《空手道小子：传奇》的首部预告片将拉尔夫·马奇奥和成龙联袂亮相</a>，首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
联邦贸易委员会宣布禁止美国隐性音乐会费用https://www.nme.com/news/music/ftc-announces-ban-on-hidden-concert-fees-in-the-us-3823392?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ftc-announces-ban-on-美国隐藏的音乐会费用Liberty DunworthWed, 18 Dec 2024 11:47:07 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3823392 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年美国 Bad Bunny 音乐会上的人群" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>新法规意味着公司必须对客户更加透明，并预先显示所有强制性费用</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ftc-announces-ban-on-hidden-concert-fees-in-the-us-3823392">FTC 宣布禁止美国隐藏音乐会费用的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年美国 Bad Bunny 音乐会上的人群" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Concert-crowd@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>美国联邦贸易委员会 (FTC) 宣布了一项针对美国隐性音乐会费用的新禁令。</p><p>新规定<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ban-on-hidden-ticket-junk-fees-suggested-by-ftc-in-us-3514090">最初于 2023 年 10 月提出</a>，禁止多个行业（包括在线门票销售）实施“垃圾费”。根据新规定，售票平台必须在购买过程中预先显示所有强制性费用，而不是仅在结账阶段显示。</p><p>它的影响也将不仅仅限于音乐会门票销售，也适用于酒店和 Airbnb，目前这些酒店和 Airbnb 都在客户结账时收取未公开的费用。</p><p>在 FTC 分享的一份新声明中，主席 Lina M. Khan（通过<a href="https://consequence.net/2024/12/ftc-bans-hidden-concert-ticket-fees/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Consequence</em></a> ）表示：“FTC 的规则将结束现场活动门票、酒店和度假租赁方面的垃圾费，为美国人节省数十亿美元和数百万美元。”浪费了几个小时。</p><p> “人们应该提前知道他们被要求支付的费用，而不用担心他们以后会背负着他们没有预算且无法避免的神秘费用。” </p><figure id="attachment_3815712" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3815712" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3815712" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ticketmaster-jonathan-raa-1.jpg" alt="票务大师" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ticketmaster-jonathan-raa-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ticketmaster-jonathan-raa-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ticketmaster-jonathan-raa-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ticketmaster-jonathan-raa-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ticketmaster-jonathan-raa-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ticketmaster-jonathan-raa-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3815712" class="wp-caption-text">售票员。图片来源：Jonathan Raa/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>新规定出台之际，今年春天早些时候，美国众议院通过了《门票法案》，以鼓励提高定价透明度并防止投机性门票。据<a href="https://www.ticketnews.com/2024/12/venue-lobby-reverses-support-seeks-to-kill-bipartisan-ticket-act/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Ticketnews</em></a>报道，该法案最快可能在本周末通过，尽管 NIVA（全国独立场馆协会）和 Live Nation/Ticketmaster 据称都在最后一刻努力将 TICKET 法案排除在持续解决支出法案之外。</p><p>虽然 FTC 已宣布禁止隐藏音乐会费用，但值得注意的是，Live Nation 和 Ticketmaster 去年回应了投诉，并于 2023 年 9 月实施了透明的全面定价模式。此后，他们继续报告从那时起到 2024 年 5 月，销售额增长 8%。</p><p>购买音乐会门票时出现的隐藏费用和意外费用问题并非美国独有， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/not-warning-oasis-fans-of-dynamic-pricing-may-be-law-breach-experts-say-3789896">英国今年也对“动态定价”的使用展开了调查。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">绿洲重聚巡演</a>的消息和随后的音乐会门票争夺战引发了这场对话。在英国和爱尔兰演出的混乱销售期间，一些粉丝失望地 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">发现，由于 Ticketmaster 的峰时定价计划，价格大幅上涨</a>，这意味着 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">在巨大的需求下价格意外上涨</a>。</p><p>强烈反对很快导致这个话题被提交给政府，工党议员鲁帕·胡克提出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticket-sellers-may-have-to-tell-fans-maximum-prices-after-oasis-dynamic-pricing-backlash-says-potential-new-law-3804848">《门票销售（体育和文化活动）法案</a>》——该法案将迫使公司与球迷分享门票的最高价格。</p><p>当时，担任伊灵中心和阿克顿议员的胡克声称，她对绿洲的票务情况感到“诽谤”，并回忆起一些<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-2025-fans-frustrated-as-theyre-held-in-long-queues-on-ticketmaster-3789320">粉丝在排队等候数小时后感到被迫支付高价的压力</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3794081" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794081" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794081" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasis@2000x1270-3.jpg" alt="Oasis 乐队的 Noel Gallagher 于 1996 年登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasis@2000x1270-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasis@2000x1270-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasis@2000x1270-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasis@2000x1270-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasis@2000x1270-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasis@2000x1270-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794081" class="wp-caption-text"> 1996 年，Oasis 乐队的 Noel Gallagher 在舞台上表演。图片来源：Stacia Timonere/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在此之前不久，英国文化大臣<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-condemns-oasis-dynamic-pricing-in-first-address-to-uk-music-industry-3802194">丽莎·南迪在她对英国音乐界的首次讲话中也谴责了绿洲英国重聚巡演的动态定价</a>。这位议员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-ticket-sales-culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-calls-for-review-into-dynamic-pricing-and-secondary-ticket-sites-3789694">在 9 月份首次呼吁对“动态定价”和二级门票网站进行审查。</a></p><p>在争议中，绿洲公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-band-say-they-at-no-time-had-any-awareness-that-dynamic-pricing-was-going-to-be-used-3790679">发表了一份声明予以回应</a>，其中写道：“绿洲公司将票务和定价的决定完全交给了他们的促销员和管理层，并且在任何时候都没有意识到将使用动态定价。”</p><p>关于音乐会门票费用的争论——即对客户缺乏透明度——仍然是英国各地讨论的话题。例如， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-hundreds-complain-to-asa-over-surge-ticket-pricing-3789875">该问题被提交给广告标准局</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-european-commission-reportedly-investigating-dynamic-pricing-amid-oasis-tickets-controversy-3790240">欧盟委员会</a>，并单独呼吁<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-ticket-sales-culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-calls-for-review-into-dynamic-pricing-and-secondary-ticket-sites-3789694">英国政府进行调查</a>。专家还建议，不警告 Oasis 粉丝动态定价<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/not-warning-oasis-fans-of-dynamic-pricing-may-be-law-breach-experts-say-3789896">可能违反消费者法</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ftc-announces-ban-on-hidden-concert-fees-in-the-us-3823392">FTC 宣布禁止美国隐藏音乐会费用的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
艾尔顿·约翰暗示新音乐：“果汁从未枯竭” https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-hints-at-new-music-the-juices-have-never-dried-up-3823383?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=elton-john-新音乐的暗示，果汁永不枯竭Tom SkinnerWed, 18 Dec 2024 11:35:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3823383 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾尔顿·约翰在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他还回顾了自己从巡演中“美妙”的退休生活</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-hints-at-new-music-the-juices-have-never-dried-up-3823383">艾尔顿·约翰 (Elton John) 的帖子暗示了新音乐：“The Juices never dryd”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾尔顿·约翰在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elton-John@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰</a>在最近接受美国电视台采访时暗示了新音乐——您可以观看下面的视频。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="471" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/elton-john-cover-interview-2021-the-lockdown-sessions-3075718"><b>NME</b>大读物——埃尔顿<b><i>·</i></b><b>约翰：“我对过去不感兴趣——甚至连埃尔顿·约翰的过去也不感兴趣”</b></a></li></ul><p>这位传奇歌手兼作曲家昨晚（12 月 17 日）作为嘉宾出现在哥伦比亚广播公司的<em>《史蒂芬·科尔伯特深夜秀》</em>中，宣传他的新纪录片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/elton-john-never-too-late-review-dodger-stadium-3821275"><em>《永远不会太晚</em></a>》。</p><p>在谈话接近尾声时，约翰回顾了他去年从现场巡演中退休的经历，他说：“这是世界上最美妙的事情……我以高亢的声音结束了——我的声音很棒，钢琴演奏很棒，乐队很棒。</p><p> “我的一生还想做一些比巡演更重要的事情。”</p><p>然而，这位“火箭人”偶像继续向歌迷保证，当他专注于家庭生活时，他“仍然会制作唱片”并且“拥有音乐的未来”。</p><p> “你会得到更多[音乐]，”约翰告诉主持人科尔伯特。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="艾尔顿·约翰：为什么改变你的生活永远不会太晚 - 加长访谈" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/W08_ZAzuiaQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “汁液从未干涸。他们永远不想干涸，因为我一直在寻找创造的东西。现在只是有空间在我自己的时间做这件事。”</p><p>他总结道：“当然会有新的埃尔顿·约翰音乐。”</p><p>您可以在上面的视频中观看完整的采访。</p><p>约翰于 2021 年发行了众星云集的合作专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/elton-john-the-lockdown-sessions-review-3073859">《The Lockdown Sessions》。</a>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-elton-john-and-brandi-carlile-new-song-never-too-late-written-for-upcoming-documentary-3813101">这位音乐家和布兰迪·卡莱尔 (Brandi Carlile) 共同发行了一首名为《Never Too Late》的新歌</a>，这是为同名医生创作的。据报道，2023 年末， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-has-reportedly-completed-a-new-album-with-brandi-carlile-3564678">两人共同完成了一张完整的唱片</a>。</p><p>此前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-reveals-he-completed-a-new-album-with-bernie-taupin-3531793">约翰透露他已经与他的长期歌曲创作伙伴伯尼·陶平（Bernie Taupin）完成了一张新唱片</a>。陶平<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-johns-surprise-new-album-reportedly-just-weeks-away-3758492">随后表示，今年五月，这位明星正准备出人意料地发行他的下一张录音室专辑</a>。</p><p>但在最近的另一次采访中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-struggling-to-record-new-music-due-to-eye-condition-i-cant-see-a-lyric-for-a-start-3815818">约翰解释说，由于严重的眼部疾病，他正在努力创作新音乐</a>。 “我一开始就看不到歌词，”他说。此后他告诉粉丝<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-expands-on-eye-infection-at-public-appearance-i-have-lost-my-eyesight-3817692">他“失去了视力”</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="埃尔顿·约翰：永远不会太晚 |官方预告片|迪士尼+" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fQGf_nJ1E9w?start=1&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>十月份， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-says-theres-not-much-of-me-left-after-missing-organs-due-to-health-issues-3799103">约翰表示，由于健康问题，经过多次手术后，“他的身体已经所剩无几了”</a> 。然而，当月晚些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-elton-john-royal-albert-hall-heritage-orchestra-watch-photos-setlist-3803980">他在伦敦皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 的特别演出中客串亮相</a>。</p><p> <em>NME</em>给予<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney</a> + 的<em>《永远不会太晚》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/elton-john-never-too-late-review-dodger-stadium-3821275">三星级评价</a>，称这部电影以“尊重和温柔”的方式“为约翰令人难以置信的表演生涯画上句号”。</p><p>与此同时，据透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-reveals-that-he-scraps-a-song-if-he-cant-nail-a-melody-in-an-hour-3821743">如果埃尔顿·约翰在一小时内无法确定旋律，他就会放弃一首歌</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-hints-at-new-music-the-juices-have-never-dried-up-3823383">艾尔顿·约翰 (Elton John) 的帖子暗示了新音乐：“The Juices never dryd”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
